OL,5, About a quarter of a million mothers   
OL,6, with young children have left their    
OL,7, jobs due to childcare pressures,       
OL,8, research by an equal rights charity    
OL,9, suggests.                              
OL,11,FLarge numbers of women were missing out
OL,12,Fon career opportunities for the same   
OL,13,Freason, the research indicated.        
OL,15,FMore mothers are working than ever     
OL,16,Fbefore, said the Fawcett Society.      
OL,18,FBut they were facing what amounted to a
OL,19,F"motherhood penalty" as their careers  
OL,20,Fweren't progressing, it said.          
